  rubyripper-0.6.2-r1.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #436848

  03 Oct 2012; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> rubyripper-0.6.2-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #436848

*rubyripper-0.6.2-r1 (18 Sep 2012)

  18 Sep 2012; Daniel Pielmeier <billie@gentoo.org>
  +rubyripper-0.6.2-r1.ebuild:
  Switch to EAPI 4 and rework dependencies. Add support for ruby19 which fixes
  bug #434122. Thanks to poncho for the report.

  07 Apr 2012; Daniel Pielmeier <billie@gentoo.org> -rubyripper-0.6.1.ebuild:
  Remove old.

  28 Jan 2012; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org> rubyripper-0.6.2.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #400811

  28 Jan 2012; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> rubyripper-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Stable for AMD64, wrt bug #400811

