*rubyripper-0.6.1 (16 Oct 2011)

  16 Oct 2011; Daniel Pielmeier <billie@gentoo.org> -rubyripper-0.5.7.ebuild,
  -rubyripper-0.6.0.ebuild, +rubyripper-0.6.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. This should fix bug #306883. Remove old.

  02 May 2011; Daniel Pielmeier <billie@gentoo.org> rubyripper-0.5.5-r1.ebuild,
  rubyripper-0.5.7.ebuild, rubyripper-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Remove unneeded dependency on dev-ruby/rcairo. Every version of rubyripper
  compiles and runs without it.

  14 Mar 2011; Daniel Pielmeier <billie@gentoo.org> rubyripper-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Use VIRTUALX_COMMAND.

*rubyripper-0.6.0 (09 Jul 2010)

  09 Jul 2010; Daniel Pielmeier <billie@gentoo.org>
  +rubyripper-0.6.0.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Version bump. Add myself to maintainers. Fixes bugs #299210 and #327233.

  06 Dec 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org>
  rubyripper-0.5.5-r1.ebuild, rubyripper-0.5.7.ebuild:
  dev-ruby/ruby-gettext is needed at build and runtime, thanks to René
  Neumann in #287956 for reporting.

  19 Oct 2009; Jonathan Callen <abcd@gentoo.org> rubyripper-0.5.5-r1.ebuild,
  rubyripper-0.5.7.ebuild:
  virtualx.eclass now has support for forcing the dependency; use it

*rubyripper-0.5.7 (30 Sep 2009)

  30 Sep 2009; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org> +rubyripper-0.5.7.ebuild:
  Add latest release (bug 280085)

