  amd64/x86 stable, bug #269294

  10 May 2009; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  rubyripper-0.5.5-r1.ebuild:
  virtualx eclass introduces USE flag X, add it to IUSE for forcing in
  profiles wrt #268980.

  10 May 2009; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  rubyripper-0.5.5-r1.ebuild:
  Require rcairo with USE flag svg wrt #250226, thanks to Diego E. Pettenò
  for reporting.

